{"type": "article", "id": 32508, "title": "他要完成艺术作品，先得往街边的房子上猛喷颜色", "description": "偶尔也会喷喷小货车。", "date": "2016-09-22T23:20:37Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 521, "name": "街头艺术"}, {"id": 1225, "name": "美国"}, {"id": 7630, "name": "艺术节"}, {"id": 33056, "name": "喷绘"}], "category": 17, "author": 619958, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 86, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160922181710gA9KIeMGL2uEQNbx.jpg", "contents": "<p class=\"\">美国艺术家 Okuda San Miguel 把位于美国阿肯色州的一栋废弃房子改造成了“万国教堂”。房子表面被喷上他标志性风格的街头风格色彩和图案——三角形、条纹、环状、波点等色块将房子完全覆盖。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"></span><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922182130zh16fHUcZTtrbOML.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663814\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"></span><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922182139rXMiKBjeJ4xpONRL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.024450\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"></span><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922182148TiBaCjf659Qw1Noq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.746944\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"></span><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922182158eQGnRLg90VZmAqBt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.737164\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"></span><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"></span><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922182338KRCo9kjIlgzBSA1V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749389\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"></span><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922182403mBGThKjlI1VdNn2U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></span></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"></span><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922182427YJORScqKmTZhVfLe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497555\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"></span><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922182757GoaTCXgOIzyMqv05.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.095355\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">美国艺术家 Okuda San Miguel。</figcaption></figure></div><p><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">这是美国</span><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/UnexpectedFS/\" style=\"text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">“The Unexpected”艺术节</a><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">的一个项目， 9 月 2 号到 11 号艺术节在阿肯色州的史密斯堡市（Fort Smith）举办，由艺术组织“64.6 downtown”和“Justkids”策划。改造后的房子位于艺术节场地的东边入口处，吸引了本地居民和艺术节参加者参观。</span></p><p>Okuda 擅长将几何图形和人体部位（如眼睛）、动物面部等元素结合。此前，摩洛哥的教堂、香港深水埗的居民楼、西班牙的货运车、意大利的幼儿园等都被喷上过他风格鲜明的创作。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922182517w4suJTEKvlCa9R5z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.151589\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">位于意大利小镇 Arcugnano 幼儿园的喷绘。</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"></span><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922182850HPMd9bxkq04WXthQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.607579\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">位于意大利小镇 Arcugnano 幼儿园的喷绘。</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"></span><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922182905pFaw6Qlf0O9JmGkW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.722494\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">位于意大利小镇 Arcugnano 幼儿园的喷绘。</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"></span><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922182919Q0Tlhx5EmjGXk3c7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.689487\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">位于意大利小镇 Arcugnano 幼儿园的喷绘。</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"></span><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922183019qGhQek1ZRT25mxwV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">位于香港深水埗的居民楼的喷绘。</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"></span><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609221830341M2IaJ5f4otyjpDx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">位于香港深水埗的居民楼的喷绘。</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">这是艺术节第二年邀请国际街头艺术家布置史密斯堡，今年共有 9 名艺术家参加，形式包括喷绘、室内外艺术装置、拍摄视频等。除了 Okuda 外，这群艺术家还包括 Alex Diaz，Faith47，Guido van Helten，Cyrcle，Maser，Bordalo II，Jaz 和 Pastel。以下是他们炫酷的作品。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"></span><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922183151ctow1F9zTXgWsnqO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667129\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Bordalo II 作品，“Fox”</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922183218hbLf2SmZkNR0z3VW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.748960\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Bordalo II 作品，“Opossum”</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922183330H54q8gLjI9evmVxD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750347\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Alex Diaz 作品。</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922183345s1Ic23ZJa08vOFPi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.276006\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Alex Diaz 作品。</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922183406914sgORNc5lvLyiI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668516\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Faith47 作品，“Royal Spirits”</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922183419ZpAPkI8J2aVt7vu1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.834951\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Guido van Helten 作品。</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922183430Wtvd0Vb365Fz8DwO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.748960\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Guido van Helten 作品。</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922183725C3H8hgFtKUIQzvjX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.644938\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Jaz and Pastel 作品，“Rapto Divino En Fort Smith”</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922183741rR5owixMT3EBqZsm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668516\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Maser 作品， “Argon”</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">图片来自：<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/art/okuda-san-miguel-universal-chapel-justkids-arkansas-09-20-2016/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a>、<a href=\"http://www.mymodernmet.com/profiles/blogs/unexpected-street-art-festival-arkansas\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">mymodernmet</a><br></p>"}